# Local working files — never committed
# NTFS "downloaded-from-internet" ADS sidecars. WSL maps the ADS colon
# to Unicode U+F03A, so a literal `*:Zone.Identifier` (ASCII colon)
# never matches; the suffix wildcard does.
*Zone.Identifier
docs/transkript*.txt
docs/**/*_2026-06-05.md
